'''Mocha Doom''' is a port of the original Doom source code to {{wp|Java (programming language)|Java}}. The conversion process has facilitated the discovery of the causes of a few obscure bugs. With the author's permission, one bugfix has been brought to [[ZDoom]] {{rev|3486}}.

